# M2b scope

M2b should be planned but not implemented during M2a.

M2b will cover:

```text
MAP
MAPCOPY
MAPSET
MAPDELETE
MAPSOURCE
MAPTARGET
DATA
MAPINVOKE input mappings
MAPINVOKE output mappings
```

M2b should also introduce:

* literal extraction policy:

  * redact,
  * include,
  * omit;
* free-text extraction policy:

  * include,
  * redact,
  * omit;
* default literal redaction;
* password and secret values never included;
* mapping source and target paths;
* transformer input/output mapping distinction;
* typed mapping operations;
* mapping summaries in Markdown.

Do not implement M2b while implementing M2a.

